  "bodyText": "The National Assistance Board was established by the National Assistance Act 1948 and abolished by the Supplementary Benefit Act 1966. It was preceded by the Unemployment Assistance Board and succeeded by the Supplementary Benefit Commission.\n\n## Other locations\n\n**Vauxhall Senior Citizens Village**\n\n- (246) 535-1808\n- (246) 535-1809\n- (246) 535-1810\n\n**Jorris Dunner Elderly Day Care Centre**\n\n- (246) 535-1801\n- (246) 535-1802\n- (246) 535-1803\n\n**St. Philip Branch** — (246) 535-1804\n\n**Speightstown Seniors Recreational Activities Programme** — (246) 535-1807"
